        <div class="text-sm max-w-md">Capture a real ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini answer for a B2B SaaS category query. Save as ai-answer-example.png in /public/assets/images/resources/earned-links-vs-paid-links/</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#64748B] italic mt-3 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
